&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JUNIOR SISTER, ENDOSCOPY UNIT, BAND 6&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The directorate of theatres and anaesthesia are looking for a healthcare professional with interest in endoscopy, to join our friendly team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be either on the register for nursing (NMC) or healthcare professionals (HCPC), with evidence of experience in the health care setting.  The successful post holder will be required to demonstrate the ability to deliver the broad range of outcomes associated with excellent clinical delivery of endoscopy services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Therefore, we are looking for a forward thinking professional who will support the Senior Endoscopy Sister to lead the day to day management of the team. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition, you will be joining a team of committed staff across the directorate which supports a wide variety of Acute District General Hospital services from endoscopy, theatres, critical care and peri operative care.  The directorate is evolving to embrace the rapidly changing landscape of the NHS, developing and empowering staff to deliver our ‘Triple R’ mission; Rural, Remote and Resourceful environments: gold standard hospital care for our Rural communities, and excellent training and services for patients in Remote and Resourceful environments. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our aim is to deliver the highest quality of care for every patient and to invest and value our staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join our team and make a real difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a full time post with a requirement to work a flexible working shift pattern.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested&lt;strong&gt; and &lt;/strong&gt;would like any further information or an informal discussion before applying then please contact Helen Byard (Directorate Matron) on 01432 355444 ext 5176, email: helen.byard@wvt.nhs.uk&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;or Fiona Goodarzi (Endoscopy Sister) on 01432 355444 ext 1508, email Fiona.goodarzi@wvt.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Interview date:  10th December 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
